products.title: Chatsworth Cream Electric Roller Blind
products.description: A modern patterned translucent fabric in 3 colour ways. You will also find this design in their vertical and roller blind collections. This bold cream and white patterned roller blind will look great in any room as it will fit in with most colour schemes and decor. The electric aspect of this blind makes it easy to use and perfect for those difficult to reach windows. Product id: db-erbx0343 fabric colour: cream headrail: durable aluminium roller tube supported by white steel brackets - top, face or side fix control type: electric control battery powered energy saving rating: er2 - medium energy saving value - effective thermal retention light filtering: yes chatsworth cream electric roller blind in white/cream.
